displayName: City of Orosh on the Mountain, Residence of the Advanced Sorcerer 1F

parameters: Wow! Your foundational research is absolutely amazing!

Advanced Mage: It is an honor to receive praise from you,
the court magician.

Advanced Mage: Someday, I would also like to conduct
research with Elatoma-san at Fortizona.

Clea: Excuse me for interrupting. I have come to deliver
the directive letter for the Archmage.
Advanced Mage: Thank you, show me.

Advanced Mage: Hmm, I understand the contents. It's
unfortunate, but I will head towards my next mission.

Court Magician Elatoma: That is unfortunate... Let's
discuss about great research together on another occasion!

Court Magician Elatoma: By the way, miss, do you have
something you need from me?

Thief Nora: I'm worried because your complexion doesn't
look good... Ugh... I'm sorry for saying something rude!

Court Magician Elatoma: Your complexion, the dark circles
under your eyes! These are the signs of an excellent mage!

Court Magician Elatoma: Well then, excuse me! I have to go
investigate Mount Scrillo next...

Mage Relm: Court Magician Elatoma... You're the mage who
defected from the enemy country Tarasa, right?

Advanced Mage: That person's understanding, knowledge, and
passion for magic are genuine. Age, gender, and place of
origin have nothing to do with being an excellent mage.

Advanced Mage: 'Oh, by the way, if you'd like, you can have
this. I've finished my research here and no longer need
it.'

Advanced Mage: Well then, shall we head towards the noble
Kasaro's place?
